dc_description_s: This data represents cranberry beds for Wood County, Wisconsin in 2018. [This dataset shows cranberry bed locations for Wood County.]
uw_supplemental_s: This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2019. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2018. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2019.Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://opendata.woodcogis.com/
